snippet.title: SQUIDS FROM SPACE - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
SQUIDS FROM SPACE is a new multiplayer team-action game from Fun Bits. Play as either Human or Squid to upgrade your base, upgrade your weapons and crush the other team in this fast-paced game of "Capture the Flag". The planet is under attack! Will you defend Earth, or conquer it?

Game:
SQUIDS FROM SPACE

Genre:
- Team-based
- Capture the Flag
- Shooter
- Action
- PvP

Website:

http://squidfromspace.com
